# tf.contrib.graph_editor.reroute_inputs

### `tf.contrib.graph_editor.reroute_inputs`

```
tf.contrib.graph_editor.reroute_inputs(sgv0, sgv1)
```


Re-route all the inputs of sgv0 to sgv1 (see reroute_inputs).
